[{"question":"But did it surprise you that in that moment, even at his young age, that he was showing such enterprising courage?","answer":"That\u0027s what\u0027s said happened and that\u0027s what\u0027s going around, that the kids made or were attempting to make a run or to escape.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":45,"aSentId":46},{"question":"What are your feelings towards the shooter himself?","answer":"My feelings towards the shooter is, it was a cowardly thing he did.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":63,"aSentId":64},{"question":"What is the most constructive, definitive thing that America\u0027s lawmakers can now do?","answer":"You know, there is no single, simple solution.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":136,"aSentId":137},{"question":"Are you really sensing, from your colleagues, that this is a tipping point?","answer":"I really am sensing that there is an openness and willingness on the part of a lot of people who never would have considered before to actually consider, for example, a ban on assault weapons which, as everybody knows, were designed for military use and right now even in the states that have them, like my state of Connecticut, and I know because I helped write the bill and then I personally defended it in court, in the trial, in the argument before state Supreme Court when it was challenged constitutionally.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":148,"aSentId":149},{"question":"Have you noticed this?","answer":"There\u0027s been an outpouring all across America of people wanting to help and to give.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":156,"aSentId":157},{"question":"Are you optimistic that there will be one before we all tumble over this cliff?","answer":"I am hopeful.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":172,"aSentId":173},{"question":"Mr. Keller, you agree with Rick Perry?","answer":"Yes, sir, I do.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":193,"aSentId":194},{"question":"And your idea is that all teachers would be armed?","answer":"ELLER: No, not at all.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":196,"aSentId":197},{"question":"Is that right?","answer":"That\u0027s correct, whether it be the weapons or the concealed carry class that I teach, either one.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":203,"aSentId":204},{"question":"Where would these teachers who are armed put the guns when they are in school?","answer":"I\u0027ve thought about that a lot in the last couple of days.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":216,"aSentId":217},{"question":"Do you sell AR-15 rifles?","answer":"When we can get them.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":227,"aSentId":228},{"question":"What is your reaction to that?","answer":"ELLER: I\u0027m just -- I\u0027m against any banning of any weapons that we are today.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":235,"aSentId":236},{"question":"Are you aware of that?","answer":"I\u0027m aware of that.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":244,"aSentId":245},{"question":"That would be your solution?","answer":"No, that\u0027s not the solution, sir.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":250,"aSentId":251},{"question":"You are aware that these weapons did unleash many, many, many bullets, are you, and killed many, many people?","answer":"My comment was that the person who is defending his place, whether it be a school or a theater, if they are trained properly, they can shoot one time and they take out the person who is spraying bullets.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":271,"aSentId":272},{"question":"This must have brought back particularly painful memories to you?","answer":"Yes, it certainly did.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":298,"aSentId":299},{"question":"But it wasn\u0027t political in anyway like the same way back in Britain, was it?","answer":"No, it wasn\u0027t.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":307,"aSentId":308},{"question":"What impact did the ban on handguns have in Britain?","answer":"Well, the level of gun crime in Britain is very low compared with the U.S. Gun crime has been falling in England every year for the last eight years.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":310,"aSentId":311},{"question":"What is your reaction to that?","answer":"I just do not understand the logic of that.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":316,"aSentId":317},{"question":"Is there any advice that you can give them, any words of comfort from somebody who\u0027s, quite literally, lived through what they\u0027ve gone through?","answer":"I think one of the main strengths that those of us who lost children in Dunblane found was being brought together.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":326,"aSentId":327},{"question":"What do you say to that?","answer":"Well, I think when a thing like this happens, obviously all questions are on the table and deserve an answer, if you can get one.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":358,"aSentId":359},{"question":"\"The Sopranos,\" much missed show, one of my favorites on television, when it came to an end, what were your honest feelings?","answer":"I was very happy.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":372,"aSentId":373},{"question":"Did you hope to have one?","answer":"Here\u0027s all I remember coherently, was that there\u0027s this Elvis Costello song \"Radio, Radio,\" the lyrics of which are \"I want to bite the hand that feeds me.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":387,"aSentId":388},{"question":"Why?","answer":"I was lucky.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":392,"aSentId":393},{"question":"Why now, quite late in your career, to plunge into the big screen?","answer":"I tried very hard.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":405,"aSentId":406},{"question":"Why did you want him?","answer":"I didn\u0027t -- I wasn\u0027t thinking about Jim originally for this, for the role of the father.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":423,"aSentId":424},{"question":"They\u0027re suggesting it\u0027s kind of autobiographical for you, that when you were young, you wanted to be a rock star?","answer":"I wanted to be a rock \u0027n\u0027 roll musician.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":431,"aSentId":432},{"question":"Didn\u0027t see yourself on stage, long hair, big guitar, strutting your stuff?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":438,"aSentId":439},{"question":"Are you ever happy with your work?","answer":"I -- I am happy.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":449,"aSentId":450},{"question":"You were?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":461,"aSentId":462},{"question":"Is that a compliment?","answer":"Yes, absolutely.","docId":"121220pmt","qSentId":466,"aSentId":467}]